giac-0.3.0 install how-to:

Downloading and unpacking:
  ftp://ftp.cs.unipr.it/pub/infrastructure/giac_unstable.tgz
  cd your-path-to-download-dir
  tar zxf giac_unstable.tgz (or gunzip -c giac_unstable.tgz | tar -xvf -)

Configuring and building:
  cd your-path-to-download-dir
  cd giac-0.3.0
  ./configure --prefix=/usr/local
  make

Installing (as root):
  su
  <give your root password>
  make install
  exit
